Package bcm.plugin

Class ClientPlugin

java.lang.Object
fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractPlugin
bcm.plugin.ClientPlugin
All Implemented Interfaces:
fr.sorbonne_u.components.PluginI, Serializable
public class ClientPlugin extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractPlugin

Description

The class ClientPlugin acts as the plugin that allows the client component to send requests to the nodes and accept the results of the requests.
